text = "Check the recipe book (R) to see how to craft items.

Drag the leaves in the Inventory (Tab) to the proper tool, then
click the check mark and follow the steps to complete the craft.

Can use arrow keys or click the arrows to craft.

Once you craft something once, you can
quickly craft it again from the recipe book.

Hover over buttons and items in menus to get descriptions."

